    <briefdescription>
<para>Callable that resolves an <ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1ecs_1_1EntityHandle" kindref="compound">EntityHandle</ref> to a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1ecs_1_1GameObject" kindref="compound">GameObject</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1ecs_1_1EntityResolver" kindref="compound">EntityResolver</ref> wraps an <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1ecs_1_1EntityManager" kindref="compound">EntityManager</ref> pointer and provides a validation-and-wrap operation: given an <ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1ecs_1_1EntityHandle" kindref="compound">EntityHandle</ref>, it checks validity via the <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1ecs_1_1EntityManager" kindref="compound">EntityManager</ref>&apos;s versioned registry and returns a lightweight <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1ecs_1_1GameObject" kindref="compound">GameObject</ref> wrapper if the handle is still alive.</para>
<para>Supports both function-call syntax and a named `find()` method.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1ecs_1_1EntityHandle" kindref="compound">EntityHandle</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
